page.title: 16HOBBIES IN LAINDON
page.content: My hobby is going in for competitions. I am quite good at them. Some of the competitions I enter are at{Radio {Basildon}near the town centre, at the basement of Brooke House. My friend Carol, goes to music every Friday. She plays the clarinet at Woodlands school. She has three lessons. Each lesson lasts half an hour. Sarah, another friend collects spoons.Some of them have politicians on them, or Prince Charles and Diana, windmills and lacemakers. You can get spoons with nearly everybody on, even Wham! She has 13 spoons and she keeps them on a special rack.
